| C | <span class="badge badge-y1">Y1</span> | <span class="badge badge-pf">PF only</span> | None | PF-background modifiers, Y1 | 17–24 |
| D | <span class="badge badge-y1">Y1</span> | <span class="badge badge-ffpf">FFPF</span> | None | PF locus test, Y1 | 25–32 |
| E | <span class="badge badge-y2">Y2</span> | <span class="badge badge-ffpf">FFPF</span> | PF | PF-independent QTL, Y2 | 33–40 |
| F | <span class="badge badge-y2">Y2</span> | <span class="badge badge-ff">FF only</span> | None | FF-background QTL, Y2 | 41–48 |
| G | <span class="badge badge-y2">Y2</span> | <span class="badge badge-pf">PF only</span> | None | PF-background modifiers, Y2 | 49–56 |
| H | <span class="badge badge-y2">Y2</span> | <span class="badge badge-ffpf">FFPF</span> | None | PF locus test, Y2 | 57–64 |
| I | <span class="badge badge-comb">Combined</span> | <span class="badge badge-ffpf">FFPF</span> | PF | Year-stable, PF-independent QTL | 65–72 |
| J | <span class="badge badge-comb">Combined</span> | <span class="badge badge-ff">FF only</span> | None | Year-stable FF QTL (highest priority) | 73–80 |

**8 traits per block (FRAC removed — redundant with PERCENT):**

| Trait | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `BIN_T1` | Binary | 1 = any budbreak at T1, 0 = none |
| `BIN_T2` | Binary | 1 = any budbreak at T2, 0 = none |
| `PERCENT_T1` | Continuous | % buds broken at T1, per-genotype mean |
| `PERCENT_T2` | Continuous | % buds broken at T2, per-genotype mean |
| `BLUE_PERCENT` | Adjusted | Block+Timepoint(+Year) fixed-effect BLUE |
| `COMP_PERCENT` | Composite | Mean of PERCENT_T1 and PERCENT_T2 |
| `PC1` | PCA score | Major axis of T1/T2 covariation (overall responsiveness) |
| `PC2` | PCA score | Contrast axis (early vs late budbreak onset timing) |

